{"tid":1414821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組手足，請準備打一場難打的戰役！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:10:59.000Z","uid":2617,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9f6badbcc24128f685366377ab65ca0a7b0d93","tid":1414821,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"引用龍戲姝巴打：<br />\n<br />\n「成個香港都知今日係全港三罷<br />\n我地和理非升級左到罷工喇（無錯我係和理非）<br />\n但點啊？777今朝10點會記者會大家都有睇<br />\n咪再強硬對我地囉<br />\n連獨立委員會都無啊<br />\n仆佢個臭街<br />\n<br />\n所以勇武升級絕對有正當性可言<br />\n我絕不割蓆」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老實講 林鄭個八婆到今時今日仲係不可一世<br />\n所有局面都一定係佢搞出黎<br />\n無論如何我都唔會怪同路人<br />\n希望文宣組都一樣 幫手繼續打呢一場戰役</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb447691de6a975ad4532e3dd54da47aa7026cda","tid":1414821,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2624850997549034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fposts%2F2624850997549034&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=8544980a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2624850997549034</a><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉：<br />\n拒絕獨立調查委員會，其實是拒絕妳自己<br />\n令香港步向玉石俱焚，其實是妳"},{"pid":"2b0067eb0cde42ed675896ddb6b18902f52bcd86","tid":1414821,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"推比文宣手足睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src